<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Security-Policy" content="default-src 'none'; style-src 'unsafe-inline'; script-src 'unsafe-inline'; img-src data:; font-src data:;">
  <title>CRO Visual Report — {{ENGAGEMENT_ID}}</title>

  <!-- ============================================================
       ASSEMBLY INSTRUCTIONS (for workflows/visual-report.md):

       1. Copy ENTIRE contents of templates/font-embed.css here verbatim
          (do NOT read or interpret — just paste the raw CSS):
       ============================================================ -->
  <style>
    {{FONT_EMBED_CSS}}
  </style>

  <!-- ============================================================
       2. Copy the design tokens + all component CSS from
          templates/components.html:
       ============================================================ -->
  <style>
    {{COMPONENT_STYLES}}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">

    <!-- [COMPONENT: report-header] -->
    <header>
      <div class="header-content">
        <div class="header-main">
          {{REPORT_HEADER}}
        </div>
        <div class="metadata">
          {{METADATA_GRID}}
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- [COMPONENT: main-grid with evidence-canvas + findings] -->
    <div class="main-grid">

      <!-- LEFT: Sticky evidence canvas with screenshot carousel + markers -->
      <section class="evidence-canvas">
        {{EVIDENCE_CANVAS}}
      </section>

      <!-- RIGHT: Scrollable finding cards -->
      <section class="findings">
        <div class="section-label">Diagnostic Insights</div>

        <!-- [COMPONENT: limitations-banner] (if screenshot-only mode) -->
        {{LIMITATIONS_BANNER}}

        <!-- [COMPONENT: finding-card] x N -->
        {{FINDING_CARDS}}

      </section>
    </div>

    <!-- [COMPONENT: summary-section] -->
    <section class="summary-section">
      {{SUMMARY_CARDS}}
    </section>

    <!-- [COMPONENT: ethics-compliance in summary card — MANDATORY] -->
    <!-- Ethics state is rendered inside the summary cards above -->

  </div>

  <!-- [COMPONENT: carousel-controller + scroll-sync] (JavaScript) -->
  {{REPORT_JS}}

</body>
</html>

<!--
  ============================================================
  ASSEMBLY NOTES:

  This template is a SKELETON. All HTML structure comes from
  templates/components.html. The workflow (workflows/visual-report.md)
  reads components.html, populates placeholders, and writes the
  completed HTML.

  DO NOT add inline CSS or custom HTML structure. All styling is
  defined in the component library's design tokens and component CSS.

  Required components from components.html:
  - Design tokens (Section 1)
  - Font embed reference (Section 2 — data from font-embed.css)
  - Report header with eyebrow + title (Section 3)
  - Metadata grid (Section 4)
  - Evidence canvas with screenshot carousel (Section 5)
  - Finding card (Section 6) — one per finding, parameterized by severity
  - Evidence tier badge (Section 7) — inline in each finding's footer
  - Metrics bar (Section 8)
  - Summary section (Section 9) — evidence confidence, severity dist, ethics
  - Limitations banner (Section 10) — for screenshot-only mode
  - Carousel controller + scroll-sync (Section 11) — JavaScript
  - Ethics compliance (Section 12) — MANDATORY, rendered in summary card
  - Escape hatches (Section 13) — for edge cases only

  REGRESSION SAFEGUARDS (check every report):
  - Ethics state present in summary card (Section 12)
  - Citation URLs clickable (rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank")
  - Evidence tier badge visible in every finding card footer
  - Evidence canvas sticky (position: sticky)
  - Screenshot images embedded as base64 data URIs
  - No analysis logic changes (output formatting only)
  ============================================================
-->
